\nHinjawadi is mainly classified in three zones,\n\n* Phase 1 \n* Phase 2 \n* Phase 3\n\n==See also==\n*[[Magarpatta]]\n*[[Kharadi]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Suburbs of Pune}}\n\n[[Category:High-technology business districts in India]]\n[[Category:Economy of Pune]]\n[[Category:Neighbourhoods in Pune]]\n[[Category:Software technology parks in Pune]]\n", "name_user": "SumitPawar2020", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eRoad transport", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hinjawadi"}
{"title_page": "2019\u201320 Moldovan Under-19 Division", "text_new": "{{ infobox football league season\n| competition                = Moldovan Under-19 Division\n| season                     = 2019\u201320\n| winners                    = \n| promoted                   =\n| relegated                  =\n| league topscorer           = \n| biggest home win           = \n| biggest away win           = \n| highest scoring            = \n| matches                   =\n| total goals                =\n| average goals              =\n| longest wins               =\n| longest unbeaten           =\n| longest losses             =\n| highest attendance         =\n| lowest attendance          =\n| average attendance         =\n| prevseason                 = [[2018\u201319 Moldovan Under-19 Division|2018\u201319]]\n| nextseason                 =\n| updated                   =\n}}\n\nThe '''2019\u201320 Moldovan Under-19 Division''' ({{lang-ro|Divizia Na\u021bional\u0103 U-19}}) is the [[Moldova]]n annual [[Association football|football]] tournament. The season began on 20 August 2019. [[FC Sheriff Tiraspol|Sheriff Tiraspol]] are the defending champions. \n\n==Stadia and locations==\n{{Location map+|Moldova|width=320|float=right|caption=Location of teams in '''2019\u201320 Divizia Na\u021bional\u0103 U-19'''.|places=\n{{Location map~|Moldova|lat=47.766667 |long=27.916667 |label=[[\u0218SSF B\u0103l\u021bi]] |position=bottom }}\n{{Location map~|Moldova|lat=47.0257   |long=28.8339   |label='''Chi\u0219in\u0103u'''|position=bottom}}\n{{Location map~|Moldova|lat=46.738611 |long=28.519167 |label=[[FC Petrocub H\u00eence\u0219ti|Petrocub]] |position=bottom }}\n{{Location map~|Moldova|lat=46.85  |long=29.633333   |label=[[FC Sheriff Tiraspol|Sheriff]] |position=bottom}}\n\n<!--FIXES FOR CHISINAU CLUBS-->\n{{Location map~|Moldova|mark=TransparentPlaceholder.png |lat=47.0 |long=26.35\n|label='''Chi\u0219in\u0103u&nbsp;teams:'''<br>[[FC Dacia-2 Buiucani|Dacia-Buiucani]]<br>[[Real Succes Chi\u0219in\u0103u|Real Succes]]<br>[[FC Zimbru Chi\u0219in\u0103u|Zimbru]]}}\n}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n!Club\n!Location\n|-\n| [[\u0218SSF B\u0103l\u021bi]] || [[B\u0103l\u021bi]]\n|-\n| [[FC Dacia-2 Buiucani|Dacia-Buiucani]] || [[Chi\u0219in\u0103u]]\n|-\n| [[FC Petrocub H\u00eence\u0219ti|Petrocub]] || [[S\u0103rata-Galben\u0103]]\n|-\n| [[Real Succes Chi\u0219in\u0103u|Real Succes]] || [[Chi\u0219in\u0103u]]\n|-\n| [[FC Sheriff Tiraspol|Sheriff]] || [[Tiraspol]]\n|-\n| [[FC Zimbru Chi\u0219in\u0103u|Zimbru]] || [[Chi\u0219in\u0103u]]\n|}\n\n==Squads==\nPlayers must be born on or after 1 January 2002, with a maximum of five players per team born between 1 January 2001 and 31 December 2001 allowed.<ref name=\"MoldovaRules\">{{cite web |url=https://www.fmf.md/sites/default/files/2019-10/documents/REGULAMENTUL%20CAMPIONATULUI%20R.%20MOLDOVA%20LA%20FOTBAL%20COPII%20SI%20JUNIORI%202019-2020.pdf|title=Regulamentul campionatului R. MOLDOVA la fotbal copii \u0219i juniori - Edi\u021bia 2019-2020 |format=pdf |publisher=[[Moldovan Football Federation]] |work=fmf.md |accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==League table==\nThe six clubs will play each other four times for a total of 20 matches per team.\n\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n|source=[https://fmf.md/home/competitii/juniori/divizia-nationala-u19-1584959466.html FMF]\n\n<!--Update team positions here-->\n|team1=SHE |team2=B\u0102L |team3=ZIM |team4=DAC |team5=REA |team6=PET\n\n<!--Update team qualifications here (defined below)-->\n|result1=CL\n\n<!--Update team results here and then (if needed) positions above. Don't forget to update the date (update parameter)-->\n| update =8 March 2020\n|win_B\u0102L=7 |draw_B\u0102L=0 |loss_B\u0102L=5 |gf_B\u0102L=32 |ga_B\u0102L=28 <!-- B\u0103l\u021bi -->\n|win_DAC=5 |draw_DAC=1 |loss_DAC=5 |gf_DAC=16 |ga_DAC=18 <!-- Dacia Buiucani -->\n|win_PET=1 |draw_PET=2 |loss_PET=9 |gf_PET=18 |ga_PET=38 <!-- Petrocub -->\n|win_REA=3 |draw_REA=2 |loss_REA=5 |gf_REA=16 |ga_REA=2