ation|canceled]] due to COVID-19 fears; it is the first time the event has been canceled in its 34-year history.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/3/6/21162247/sxsw-2020-cancelled-coronavirus-austin-texas-virus-fears-public-health-event|work=The Verge|date=March 6, 2020|accessdate=March 7, 2020|title=SXSW 2020 canceled due to coronavirus}}</ref>\n**President Trump announces Representative [[Mark_Meadows_(North_Carolina_politician)|Mark Meadows]] will succeed [[Mick Mulvaney]] as [[White House Chief of Staff]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Trump replaces Mick Mulvaney with Mark Meadows as chief of staff |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/03/06/politics/trump-mulvaney-out/index.html|publisher=CNN|date=March 7, 2020|accessdate=March 7, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[March 7]] &ndash; COVID-19 pandemic: [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Washington, D.C.|Washington, D.C.]] records its first case of COVID-19.<ref>{{cite web |title=Washington, D.C., has first 'presumptive positive' test for coronavirus|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-washingtondc/washington-d-c-has-first-presumptive-positive-test-for-coronavirus-idUSKBN20U0ZY|publisher=Reuters|date=March 7, 2020 |accessdate=March 8, 2020}}</ref>\n* [[March 9]]\n**[[2020 stock market crash#Black Monday (9 March)|Black Monday 2020]]: Share prices fall sharply, in response to economic concerns and the impact of COVID-19. The Dow Jones industrial average plunges more than 2,000 points, its biggest ever fall in intraday trading.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-51796806|title=Black Monday: Shares face biggest fall since financial crisis|website=BBC News|language=en|date=March 9, 2020|access-date=March 9, 2020}}</ref> [[Oil prices]] plunge by as much as 30% in early trading, the biggest fall since 1991, after Saudi Arabia launches a [[2020 Russia\u2013Saudi Arabia oil price war|price war]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Oil prices plunge as much as 30% after OPEC deal failure sparks price war |ur