harram]] (Muslim New Year)\n* August 23 \u2013 [[Indianapolis 500]], Indianapolis, IN.\n* August 24\u201427 \u2013 The [[2020 Republican National Convention|Republican National Convention]] is planned to be held in [[Charlotte]], [[North Carolina]].<ref>[https://www.charlottesgotalot.com/2020-republican-national-convention 2020 Republican National Convention in Charlotte, NC<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>\n*August 28\u201430 \u2013 [[Electric Zoo]], [[Electronic music|Electronic music festival]], Randall's Island, New York, NY.<ref name=festivals/>\n*August 30 \u2013 September 7 \u2013 [[Burning Man]] festival, [[Black Rock Desert]], Nevada.<ref name=festivals/>\n*August ''(date undefined)'' \u2013 [[Afropunk Festival]], Brooklyn, NY.<ref name=festivals/>\n\n=== September ===\n*September 5 \u2013 [[Kentucky Derby]], [[Churchill Downs]], Louisville, KY. Rescheduled from May 2\n*September 7 \u2013 [[Labor Day]]\n*September 11 \u2013 [[Patriot Day]]\n*September 13 \u2013 [[National Grandparents Day]]\n*September 14 \u2013 [[Boston Marathon]]. Rescheduled from April 20\n*September 19 \u2013 [[Rosh Hashanah]] (Jewish New Year)\n*September 22 \u2013 [[September equinox|Fall equinox]]\n*September 28 \u2013 [[Yom Kippur]] (Jewish Day of Atonement)\n\n=== October ===\n*October 2\u20144 \u2013 [[Electric Daisy Carnival]], Las Vegas, Nevada.<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.festicket.com/magazine/discover/top-festivals-usa/ |title = Electric Daisy Carnival |author = <!--Not stated--> |website = insomniac.com |publisher = Insomniac Holdings, LLC|access-date = 2020-04-05 }}</ref>\n*October 4\u20146 \u2013 [[Austin City Limits Music Festival]], part one, [[Zilker Park]], Austin, TX.<ref name=festivals/>\n*October 9\u201411 \u2013 [[Coachella Valley Music and Arts Festival]], first part, [[Indio, California]]. Rescheduled from April 10\u201312<ref name=festivals>{{citation|website=festicket.com |title=TOP 15: Music Festivals in the USA 2020|accessdate=Dec 22, 2019|url=https:/