-top-100-friday-cable-originals-9-25-2015.html|title=Top 100 Friday Cable Originals: 9.25.2015|author=Mitch Metcalf|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=September 15, 2014|access-date=December 2, 2016}}</ref>\n| viewers3          = {{decimals|{{#expr:((\n                      2.190 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 1 -->\n                      1.974 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 2 -->\n                      1.195 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 3 -->\n                      1.709 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 4 -->\n                      2.063 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 5 -->\n                      1.969 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 6 -->\n                      1.860 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 7 -->\n                      1.680 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 8 -->\n                      1.438 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 9 -->\n                      1.971 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 10 -->\n                      2.142 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 11 -->\n                      1.722 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 12 -->\n                      1.826 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 13 -->\n                      1.809 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 14 -->\n                      2.194 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 15 -->\n                      1.698 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 16 -->\n                      1.759 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 17 -->\n                      1.631 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 18 -->\n                      1.954 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 19 -->\n                      1.614 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 20 -->\n                      2.012 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 21 -->\n                      1.794 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 22 -->\n                      2.146   <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 23 -->\n                              <!-- end of raw data; please make sure one plus sign (+) 